SUMMARY:Cubs Summer Camp
DESCRIPTION:Three days under canvas at Pioneer Camp — Friday afternoon arrival\, Sunday afternoon collection. The Pack will be running a mix of campcraft\, water activities and the all-time-favourite night hike.\nKit list and consent forms will be sent home four weeks ahead of camp. Bursary support is available — speak to Akela in confidence if cost would otherwise stop your Cub joining us.\n
LOCATION:Pioneer Camp\, Buckinghamshire
